thread.title: Lauryn

author: Lauryn
title: Lauryn
text: Peaches Boutique has a huge selection of dresses. I was shopping for a prom dress and I found many options that were appealing to me. The workers were also very helpful and nice. The workers helped me to pick my prom dress because of how convincing they were and because of all of the compliments. I love the system that they use to get everybody in and out of the store as well. It was crowded but it went very smoothly. Everything's definitely peachy at Peaches.
